node.text: So thankful to be sharing my love for horses with my kids! It’s a dream come true. ✨ taking these photos was so fun! @alittlestoryphotography

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jade (A Spoonful of Style) on July 15, 2021 tagging @alittlestoryphotography. May be an image of 1 person, child, standing, horse and outdoors.

node.text: “Man it feels good to be country again” 💗 I heard that @thomasrhettakins song a couple of months ago while we were up at my sisters ranch and it brought me to tears. I can’t explain it but this just feels like home to me. It feels like this is where I belong. I wouldn’t change A thing. I am thankful for every experience I have had that has lead me back here! But man it feels good to be country again! 💗💗 @alittlestoryphotography I’m blown away at these!

node.text: Scott party of 6! We are so excited to introduce all of you to our new horse Monte! 🐎 I am so excited to share this new adventure with you guys! Sharing lots more about him in stories! Thank you @alittlestoryphotography for capturing these pictures for us. It rained the entire time we were doing photos and you can’t even really tell thanks to @alittlestoryphotography.
